api_list.name: Status
api_list.description: with this endpoint you can check the status for  certain job, it requires the job_id.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://midjourney-auto-upscale.p.rapidapi.com/status/01ha4e53p8rwfped4qtjcsk7kx"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "midjourney-auto-upscale.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
